‐Okay, calm down, Alison.

00:18.101 --> 00:19.394
No. Nothing is sacred to you.
Nothing.

00:19.478 --> 00:21.396
‐[Eden] Helen Solloway?
‐Hi.

00:21.480 --> 00:24.316
Eden Ellery.
I‐I was Noah's publicist.

00:24.399 --> 00:26.777
Bad idea.

00:26.860 --> 00:28.445
We're working
together.

00:28.528 --> 00:29.029
[Helen] <i>I think
they were sleeping together.</i>

00:29.112 --> 00:29.696
