a‐a scene of rape.

01:01.937 --> 01:03.689
Are you fucking kidding me?!

01:03.772 --> 01:04.982
Can I help you?

01:05.065 --> 01:06.108
You must be Helen.
I'm Christianna.

01:06.191 --> 01:08.026
I'm sorry. Should I know you?

01:08.110 --> 01:08.777
‐I'm his daughter.
‐[Sasha] <i>Well, that's hardly</i>

01:08.860 --> 01:11.154
