‐No.

01:11.238 --> 01:13.240
Not now that it's
inconvenient for you.

01:13.323 --> 01:15.284
‐How much?!
‐$25,000.

01:15.367 --> 01:19.997
She shows up, pretends
she wants a... relationship.

01:20.080 --> 01:21.832
‐Oh, my God.
‐So do you like it?

01:21.915 --> 01:23.458
Are you kidding me?!

01:23.542 --> 01:25.460
‐You're a genius.
‐Oh.

01:25.544 --> 01:26.128
To new friends and
new beginnings.

01:26.211 --> 01:29.298
‐Cheers.
‐Cheers. [laughs]

01:29.381 --> 01:30.841
