01:30.924 --> 01:32.467
What about Barry's movie?

01:32.551 --> 01:33.510
I can't make it work.

01:33.594 --> 01:34.595
I'm sorry.

01:34.678 --> 01:36.930
Hello, little love.

01:37.014 --> 01:37.306
Hi, Mom.

01:39.558 --> 01:40.684
