<i>Can you watch him for me?</i>

01:40.767 --> 01:43.478
My mom was supposed to do it,
but she just cancelled.

01:43.562 --> 01:44.354
She has the flu
or something.

01:44.438 --> 01:46.440
Oh, I'd love to,
but I have a work thing.

01:47.983 --> 01:48.984
