03:23.912 --> 03:25.372
contribute to the firm?

03:25.455 --> 03:29.042
Um... I know I don't
have a design degree,

03:29.126 --> 03:31.378
or an, um, NCIDQ certification,

03:31.461 --> 03:35.132
but I've been putting houses
together my entire life.

03:35.215 --> 03:37.217
And since I've started
doing it professionally,

03:37.300 --> 03:39.469
my client list has grown
pretty quickly.

03:39.553 --> 03:41.596
I started off with one client,
and since‐‐

03:41.680 --> 03:43.014
I don't know‐‐
in the past few months,

03:43.098 --> 03:45.767
I've already done
five other homes.

03:45.851 --> 03:47.602
All on my own, so...

03:47.686 --> 03:49.729
