of your other clients?

03:49.813 --> 03:52.065
Well...

03:52.149 --> 03:53.817
Sasha Mann,

03:53.900 --> 03:55.569
Carolina Wineman.

03:55.652 --> 03:59.448
Look, my son, uh,
just put together this

03:59.531 --> 04:01.950
