04:22.554 --> 04:25.307
[Hailey] Oh. Bringing your
grand total up to five.

04:27.225 --> 04:30.145
I can't see who it is, though.

04:30.228 --> 04:32.439
They're probably private.
You have to follow them back.

04:32.522 --> 04:34.816
Okay. Anyway, um, getting back

04:34.900 --> 04:37.152
to what I think I could
contribute to the firm...

04:37.235 --> 04:38.528
[Rebecca]
Amy

04:38.612 --> 04:40.238
is actually very good friends

04:40.322 --> 04:41.990
with Barry and Carolina Wineman.

04:42.073 --> 04:43.909
[Hailey] The competition for
the open designer position

04:43.992 --> 04:46.328
is pretty fierce.

04:46.411 --> 04:48.663
A recommendation from Carolina
would go a long way

04:48.747 --> 04:49.664
in moving your résumé

04:49.748 --> 04:52.167
to the top of the huge
stack on Amy's desk.

04:52.250 --> 04:54.294
Why don't you call Carolina
right now?

04:54.377 --> 04:56.546
That is a great idea.

04:56.630 --> 04:57.214
[chuckles softly]

04:57.297 --> 04:58.590
I think she's on vacation.

04:58.673 --> 05:00.967
Yeah.

05:01.051 --> 05:01.927
Far away.

05:02.010 --> 05:05.388
Like, unreachable, really.

05:05.472 --> 05:06.848
So...

05:06.932 --> 05:08.975
[woman]
Who's unreachable?

05:09.059 --> 05:10.352
‐Amy!
‐You're back early!

05:10.435 --> 05:11.561
Hi.

05:11.645 --> 05:13.271
Hi. I'm Helen.

05:13.355 --> 05:14.940
We were just talking
about Carolina Wineman.

05:15.023 --> 05:16.775
‐Mm.
‐She's in town.

05:16.858 --> 05:19.069
They were supposed to leave
to shoot Barry's new movie,

05:19.152 --> 05:21.196
but the funding fell out
at the last minute,

05:21.279 --> 05:23.532
poor bastard.
I'll tell you this, though.

05:23.615 --> 05:25.367
I was just at his 60th
birthday party about a month

05:25.450 --> 05:28.912
or so ago, and whoever
redid their house

05:28.995 --> 05:30.330
did a hell of a job.

05:30.413 --> 05:32.207
Helen claims that
was her work.

05:32.290 --> 05:34.042
I'm sorry. What did
you say your name was?

05:34.125 --> 05:35.627
Helen Butler.

05:35.710 --> 05:37.045
Oh, God.

05:37.128 --> 05:40.173
Carolina told me all about you.

05:40.257 --> 05:41.716
She did?

05:41.800 --> 05:42.592
She said you're a genius.

05:47.055 --> 05:49.182
She's a great lady.

05:50.809 --> 05:52.686
[car alarm system chirps]

05:57.440 --> 05:58.567
[sighs heavily]

06:01.695 --> 06:03.113
[phone buzzes]

06:10.036 --> 06:12.205
‐[phone buzzes]
‐Oh.

06:13.248 --> 06:14.666
Hi.

06:14.749 --> 06:16.501
[Whitney]
<i>♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</i>

06:16.585 --> 06:18.169
<i>♪ Happy birthday! ♪</i>

06:18.253 --> 06:20.755
Okay, all right.
Great. Don't remind me.

06:20.839 --> 06:23.091
<i>Mom, come on. I know this
isn't your favorite day ever,</i>

06:23.174 --> 06:23.842
<i>but can we try
to be a little happy?</i>

06:23.925 --> 06:26.344
Yes, I am happy.

06:26.428 --> 06:27.929
I just got that job.

06:28.013 --> 06:29.764
<i>Oh, my God! Congratulations!</i>

06:29.848 --> 06:31.433
Thank you.

06:31.516 --> 06:33.268
I'm really just relieved.

06:33.351 --> 06:35.437
I mean, hopefully,
this will cover

06:35.520 --> 06:37.147
Stacey and Trevor's tuitions,

06:37.230 --> 06:39.232
and I won't have
to sell the house.

06:39.316 --> 06:41.651
Uh, anyway, I'm sorry that I
couldn't go out there with you.

06:41.735 --> 06:43.028
I just couldn't
turn down this interview.

06:43.111 --> 06:44.821
<i>Mom, it's okay.</i>

06:44.905 --> 06:45.906
<i>Dad and I have the wedding
thing totally covered.</i>

06:45.989 --> 06:47.324
You do?

06:47.407 --> 06:50.076
<i>Yeah, he's actually
been amazing.</i>

06:50.160 --> 06:52.579
<i>We‐we got a tent, the rentals,
we found a DJ, we have flowers.</i>

06:55.874 --> 06:57.459
Wow. Okay, um...

06:57.542 --> 06:59.002
[laughing]
Great.

06:59.085 --> 07:00.211
I guess when you get back,

07:00.295 --> 07:01.755
we'll find you
the perfect dress.

07:01.838 --> 07:03.089
<i>Oh, no, we found a dress.</i>

07:03.173 --> 07:04.466
You did?

07:04.549 --> 07:06.551
<i>Yeah. It's yours!</i>

07:06.635 --> 07:09.012
Grandma showed you my dress?
She hated that dress.

07:09.095 --> 07:11.139
<i>No, no, no, it was
Dad's idea. Oh, shit.</i>

07:11.222 --> 07:12.599
<i>I should go. We're heading
back to the city.</i>

07:12.682 --> 07:14.225
<i>I love you so much!
Happy birthday!</i>

07:14.309 --> 07:15.310
